## ==> EXPERIENCED SKILLS (经验技能)

##### Experimental skills: 
> 1. Cloning with different strategies (**<font color="green">Golden Braid</font>**, Gateway, and classical) (多种分子克隆技术);
2. Creating mutants by **<font color="green">CRISPR-Cas9 system</font>** and genotyping in plant (CRISPR-Cas9应用于番茄突变体的获得及鉴定);
3. Isolating and quantifying DNA and RNA for large-scale sequencing (大规模测序实验DNA和RNA制备);
4. **<font color="green">Implementing chromatin immunoprecipitation</font>** for histone modifications (染色质免疫共沉淀ChIP-seq技术);
5. Detecting fluorescence with stereo and **<font color="green">confocal microscope</font>** (LEICA SP2 AOBS) (高分辨率(荧光)显微镜的操作使用);
6. Regular molecular biology experiments (WB,qRT-PCR and Y2H ...);
7. Tomato transformation technique (番茄遗传转化);

##### Analysis skills: 
> 1. **<font color="green">Performing RNA-seq, ChIP-seq and BS-seq data analysis in Unix cluster</font>** (Unix下RNA-seq，ChIP-seq和BS-seq数据的基本生物信息学操作); 
2. **<font color="green">Analyzing data in R environment with data cleaning, data normalization, data processing and plots generating</font>using various packages (dplyr, DEseq2, ggplot2 and DSS ...)** (运用不同packages在R中实现数据整理，分析及作图)
